---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About | Morshadun Nur - Shopify Developer" description="Learn about Morshadun Nur's experience, skills, and approach to Shopify development and e-commerce solutions.">
  <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-secondary text-white py-12">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">About Me</h1>
      <p class="text-xl">Shopify Expert & Full Stack Developer with a passion for e-commerce</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
      <!-- Profile Image and Quick Info -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-1">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <img src="/images/profile.png" alt="Morshadun Nur" class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg mb-6" />
          
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Shopify Developer | Full-Stack Developer | Laravel Expert</h2>
          
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-primary mr-3" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 13.255A23.931 23.931 0 0112 15c-3.183 0-6.22-.62-9-1.745M16 6V4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-4a2 2 0 00-2 2v2m4 6h.01M5 20h14a2 2 0 002-2V8a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700"> Over 7+ years of Web Development experience and 3+ years of Shopify experience.</span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-primary mr-3" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 12l2-2m0 0l7-7 7 7M5 10v10a1 1 0 001 1h3m10-11l2 2m-2-2v10a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3m-6 0a1 1 0 001-1v-4a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v4a1 1 0 001 1m-6 0h6" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700">Located in Dhaka, Bangladesh</span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-primary mr-3" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700">Available for remote work</span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-primary mr-3" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
              </svg>
              <a href="mailto:me@morshadunnur.me" class="text-primary hover:text-secondary">me@morshadunnur.me</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="mt-6 pt-6 border-t border-gray-200">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Core Skills</h3>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-gray-800 text-sm rounded-full">Shopify</span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-gray-800 text-sm rounded-full">Shopify Theme</span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-gray-800 text-sm rounded-full">Shopify App</span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-gray-800 text-sm rounded-full">Liquid</span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-gray-800 text-sm rounded-full">JavaScript</span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-gray-800 text-sm rounded-full">TypeScript</span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-gray-800 text-sm rounded-full">PHP</span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-gray-800 text-sm rounded-full">Node.js</span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-gray-800 text-sm rounded-full">React</span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-gray-800 text-sm rounded-full">Remix</span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-gray-800 text-sm rounded-full">Vue</span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-gray-800 text-sm rounded-full">Laravel</span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-gray-800 text-sm rounded-full">GraphQL</span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-gray-800 text-sm rounded-full">MySQL</span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-gray-800 text-sm rounded-full">PostgreSQL</span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-gray-800 text-sm rounded-full">Docker</span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-gray-800 text-sm rounded-full">AWS</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Main Content -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-2">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">My Journey</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            Hello! I'm Morshad, a dedicated Shopify Expert and Full Stack Developer with over 5 years of experience in creating custom e-commerce solutions. My journey in web development began with a fascination for how online businesses operate and grow.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            After completing my degree in Computer Science, I specialized in e-commerce development, focusing primarily on the Shopify platform. Over the years, I've helped numerous businesses establish and optimize their online presence, from small boutiques to large retail operations.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            My approach combines technical expertise with a deep understanding of e-commerce best practices. I believe that a successful online store needs both flawless functionality and strategic design to convert visitors into customers.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">What I Do</h2>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Shopify Store Development</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">
                I build custom Shopify stores that are tailored to your brand's unique needs. From selecting the right theme to customizing every aspect of the user experience, I ensure your store stands out from the competition.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Theme Customization</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">
                I transform standard Shopify themes into unique storefronts that reflect your brand identity. My customizations focus on both aesthetics and functionality to create a seamless shopping experience.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">App Integration</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">
                I integrate and customize third-party apps to extend your store's functionality. From marketing tools to inventory management systems, I ensure all components work together flawlessly.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Performance Optimization</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">
                I optimize your Shopify store for speed and performance, ensuring fast load times and smooth operation. This includes image optimization, code minification, and strategic resource loading.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">My Approach</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            I believe in a collaborative approach to development. Your input and vision are essential to creating a store that truly represents your brand. My process involves:
          </p>
          
          <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700 mb-4 pl-4">
            <li><span class="font-medium">Discovery:</span> Understanding your business, goals, and target audience</li>
            <li><span class="font-medium">Planning:</span> Creating a detailed roadmap for your project</li>
            <li><span class="font-medium">Design:</span> Developing the visual and functional aspects of your store</li>
            <li><span class="font-medium">Development:</span> Building and customizing your Shopify store</li>
            <li><span class="font-medium">Testing:</span> Ensuring everything works perfectly across all devices</li>
            <li><span class="font-medium">Launch:</span> Going live with your new or improved store</li>
            <li><span class="font-medium">Support:</span> Providing ongoing assistance and optimization</li>
          </ol>
          
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Ready to take your Shopify store to the next level? <a href="/contact" class="text-primary hover:text-secondary font-medium">Let's talk about your project</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>